The '''''Sad-dar'''''{{Pronunciation-needed}}<!-- as IPA --> or ''Saddar'', literally ''Hundred Doors'' or chapters is a [[Persian language|Persian]] book about [[Zoroastrianism]]. The hundred chapters are guidelines that [[Zoroastrian]]s should follow. 

[[Sanskrit]] cognate is ''Shat-Dwar'' (Shat=Hundred, Dwar=Door)

