'''Sri Guru Singh Sabha Malton''' is a [[gurudwara]] ([[Sikhism|Sikh]] temple) located in [[Malton, Ontario]], Canada. A [[gurdwara]] ({{lang-pa|ਗੁਰਦੁਆਰਾ}}, ''{{IAST|gurdu'ārā}}'' or {{lang|pa|ਗੁਰਦਵਾਰਾ}}, ''{{IAST|gurdvārā}}''), meaning "the doorway to the Guru", is the [[Sikh]] place of worship and may be referred to as a Sikh temple.
