'''Tales from the Leather Nun''' was an American [[underground comics|underground comic]] published by [[Last Gasp]] in 1973. It was a one-shot anthology of bizarre, violent and perverted stories featuring nuns by [[Dave Sheridan (artist)|Dave Sheridan]], [[Robert Crumb]], [[Spain Rodriguez]], [[Jaxon]], [[Roger Brand]], and [[Pat Ryan (cartoonist)|Pat Ryan]].<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=nvFGlkTMAccC&pg=PA18&dq=%2B%22Tales+from+the+Leather+Nun%22&hl=en&ei=ePnXTeHQMcnegQe76eVX&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=%2B%22Tales%20from%20the%20Leather%20Nun%22&f=false "Thrill to Stories of Graphic Lust!"] by David Kerekes. ''Critical Vision: Random Essays and Tracts Concerning Sex, Religion, Death'' (Stockport, UK: Headpress, 1995), p. 18. Retrieved May 21, 2011.</ref>
[[Deborah Harry]] is seen reading the comic in the 1992 movie ''[[Intimate Stranger (1992 film)|Intimate Stranger]]''.
